CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Terreno Realty Corp is a real estate investment trust primarily engaged in the acquisition ownership and operation of industrial real estate in the U.S. Warehouse properties located in large densely-populated urban areas along the U.S. coastline comprise the vast majority of the companys portfolio. The markets of Los Angeles Northern New Jersey and New York City San Francisco Bay Area Seattle Miami and Washington DC are the companys major markets. Terreno derives nearly all of its revenue in the form of rental income from tenants. Terrenos largest customers are large manufacturers and distributors such as Amazon FedEx the U.S. Government Northrop Grumman Systems and more. The company controls a smaller number of light industrial and research and development facilities.
